{
 "name": "RPlog_Just_Play_the_Game",
 "title": "Just Play the Game",
 "summary": "On break from the war at the smuggler settlement of Esau's Ridge on Tholatin, New Republic pilot Raxis L'ygr is playing sabacc in a cantina when he spots Liza Molokai, an Imperial pilot he has dueled against in the sky. When a Chiss patron menaces the unarmed Liza, Raxis steps in and invites her to his table, revealing himself as her old comm-channel adversary, Ghost Three. Over cards, drinks, and cigarettes the two enemies share an unexpectedly candid conversation about loyalty, idealism, death in war, and the toll the conflict takes on them both. Raxis quietly lets Liza win the hand, and as she leaves he walks her safely to the spaceport -- the two parting on warm terms despite knowing they may try to kill each other the next time they meet.",
